01:40:59.760 --> 01:41:00.160
E.

01:41:04.598 --> 01:41:06.674
Quarantine.

01:41:44.680 --> 01:41:47.877
General McEwan. Colonel Bertrang.
Thanks for coming down.

01:41:47.981 --> 01:41:53.432
- Odie, you reading me OK?
- Yeah, Howard. You're A-OK.

01:41:57.234 --> 01:42:02.655
All right, flight controls are active.
She's all yours.

01:42:09.288 --> 01:42:11.697
She's spotless, Odie.
No wiggle on the wheel or throttles.

01:42:11.801 --> 01:42:13.867
Take it easy.

01:42:30.518 --> 01:42:34.341
- How does she sound, Howard?
- She's whispering to me, buddy.

01:42:34.445 --> 01:42:37.225
All right, make her sing.

01:42:57.086 --> 01:43:00.532
Well, Odie, she can fly.
Congratulations.

01:43:00.636 --> 01:43:05.831
I'm glad to hear it. Retract landing gear and
climb to 5,000 feet on a heading of 2-7-0.

01:43:05.935 --> 01:43:12.381
Retracting landing gear and climbing
to 5,000 feet on a heading 2-7-0.

01:43:16.397 --> 01:43:18.677
- Jesus, she's fast.
- What's your airspeed, Howard?

01:43:18.781 --> 01:43:22.553
- 292.
- All right, take her back to 200.

01:43:22.657 --> 01:43:24.278
No damn way.

01:43:49.930 --> 01:43:51.751
All right, Howard, we gotta bring her home.

01:43:51.855 --> 01:43:55.173
Scheduled time of one hour and 45
minutes has elapsed. Set course for 0-9-0.

01:43:55.277 --> 01:44:00.341
- Give me ten more minutes. Roger that.
- Negative. Howard, bring her home.

01:44:00.445 --> 01:44:01.634
OK. OK.

01:44:01.738 --> 01:44:06.684
Setting course for 0-9-0.

01:44:06.788 --> 01:44:08.939
Preparing to descend.

01:44:12.411 --> 01:44:15.910
- Jesus.
- What is it, Howard?

01:44:16.957 --> 01:44:20.614
The right wing just dipped.
I'm losing starboard engine.

01:44:20.718 --> 01:44:23.658
Increasing power to 2800 rpm.

01:44:23.762 --> 01:44:25.410
Cutting back.

01:44:25.514 --> 01:44:27.714
Increasing starboard engine only.

01:44:28.803 --> 01:44:31.960
Cutting back.
I'm losing altitude.

01:44:32.064 --> 01:44:35.585
Howard, check starboard engine
manifold pressure.

01:44:35.690 --> 01:44:39.009
- It's good, but rpms are low.
- Are both starboard props turning?

01:44:39.113 --> 01:44:40.713
Hold on.

01:44:40.907 --> 01:44:43.928
It looks like they are, but she's pulling me
back and starboard, Odie.

01:44:44.032 --> 01:44:47.721
- How bad is your cross control?
- I'm at full left rudder and full left aileron,

01:44:47.826 --> 01:44:50.269
but she won't stay level.
Goddamn it.

01:44:50.373 --> 01:44:53.357
- Howard, give us your position.
- 2,000 feet over...

01:44:53.462 --> 01:44:57.525
Oh, Christ, I don't know.
Beverly Hills. 1,500 feet.

01:44:57.629 --> 01:44:59.450
We're going down.

01:45:00.334 --> 01:45:03.947
I'm gonna try for the Wilshire Country
Club. Ninth hole. You reading me?

01:45:04.051 --> 01:45:08.091
Wilshire Country Club. Copy that.
Howard, reduce engines to one thousand.

01:45:08.717 --> 01:45:11.165
I'm going down.

01:45:11.269 --> 01:45:13.753
I'm not gonna make it, buddy.

01:45:19.979 --> 01:45:21.141
Goddamn it.

01:47:24.353 --> 01:47:27.844
Is there anyone else inside?
Is there anyone else?

01:47:27.948 --> 01:47:28.548
No.

01:47:33.446 --> 01:47:36.392
I'm Howard Hughes, the aviator.

01:47:36.496 --> 01:47:38.096
Come on.

01:47:45.791 --> 01:47:49.032
Every inch of wiring and fluid connection...

01:47:49.136 --> 01:47:51.825
He has burns to 78 per cent of his body.

01:47:51.930 --> 01:47:54.997
Nine ribs are shattered.
Not broken, shattered.

01:47:55.102 --> 01:47:59.626
As are his nose, his chin, his cheek,
his left knee, his left elbow.

01:47:59.730 --> 01:48:02.835
He has 60 lacerations on his face
to the bone.

01:48:02.940 --> 01:48:05.797
His chest was crushed,
so his left lung has collapsed

01:48:05.901 --> 01:48:10.346
and his heart has shifted entirely
to the right side of his chest cavity.

01:48:10.450 --> 01:48:12.344
Jesus, God.

01:48:12.448 --> 01:48:15.806
He's getting blood transfusions now, but...

01:48:15.910 --> 01:48:19.396
- Whose blood?
- I'm sorry?

01:48:19.500 --> 01:48:22.816
- Whose blood?
- From our stock.

01:48:22.920 --> 01:48:24.776
He's not gonna like that.

01:48:24.880 --> 01:48:30.571
Mr Dietrich, I doubt he's ever
gonna like or dislike anything again.

01:48:30.676 --> 01:48:33.042
I'm terribly sorry.

01:49:01.281 --> 01:49:03.268
Orange juice.

01:49:03.372 --> 01:49:04.772
It's...

01:49:06.212 --> 01:49:09.453
It's not fresh from the kitchen, so I...

01:49:10.499 --> 01:49:14.627
I have them make it here so I can see.

01:49:19.716 --> 01:49:21.792
Look at me.

01:49:24.304 --> 01:49:28.000
I'm a monster.
Yeah.

01:49:28.104 --> 01:49:31.800
Orange juice has nutritional value.

01:49:32.854 --> 01:49:38.183
There's some flies
outside my window, though.

01:49:38.287 --> 01:49:39.287
So...

01:49:42.072 --> 01:49:44.148
little Howard likes...

01:49:46.076 --> 01:49:47.476
citrus.

01:49:49.127 --> 01:49:51.197
Don't he just?

01:49:54.126 --> 01:49:55.726
Tell me.

01:49:57.471 --> 01:50:01.325
An oil seal ripped off
the starboard rear propeller.

01:50:01.429 --> 01:50:05.332
When the pressure dropped,
the prop reversed pitch.

01:50:05.436 --> 01:50:07.627
Do you understand me?

01:50:07.731 --> 01:50:12.712
Howard, I'm sorry to have to tell you
this now, but there's something else.

01:50:12.816 --> 01:50:15.267
- You following me?
- Yeah.

01:50:17.065 --> 01:50:22.892
The Air Force cancelled
the contract on the Hercules.

01:50:22.996 --> 01:50:28.687
The war's over now,
and they say they don't need it any more.

01:50:28.792 --> 01:50:33.403
I have to know what you want me to do.
Should I release the staff?

01:50:33.507 --> 01:50:35.507
How far...

01:50:36.005 --> 01:50:38.955
from finishing?

01:50:40.130 --> 01:50:42.871
- About six months.
- No, no.

01:50:42.976 --> 01:50:44.776
In money.

01:50:48.222 --> 01:50:52.302
Seven million.
Maybe more.

01:50:58.023 --> 01:50:59.823
Build it.

01:51:00.952 --> 01:51:03.952
Build it, Odie.

01:51:04.787 --> 01:51:06.187
Howard,

01:51:06.915 --> 01:51:10.941
a Constellation crashed
outside Reading, Pennsylvania.

01:51:11.045 --> 01:51:14.903
The Civil Aeronautics Board
